CBRE are excited to present to the market for lease, 46-56 Gosport Street, Hemmant. Hemmant is situated approx. 15 kilometres south east of the Brisbane CBD and is strategically located between the Port of Brisbane and Gateway Motorway offering easy access for any fabrication or transport operations. Hemmant remains one of the most sought after locations for most transport/distribution businesses.

Some of the features of this site are: 

- 1,037sqm office accommodation split over two levels
- 11,594sqm of high bay warehouse (10.5m internal clearance)
- Approx. 30,000sqm of dedicated hardstand ideal for trucks and container storage
- Nine overhead gantry cranes
- Duel crossovers with security fence 
- Significant power supply
- Flexible tenancies available from 1,000sqm warehouse 
- Building to undergo refurbishment 

46-56 Gosport Street, Hemmant is a facility not to be missed as this is an opportunity to secure one of the best transport facilities within the Port of Brisbane region.

CBRE are pleased to present to the market for Sale 16 Akuna Court, Hemmant. This property is located in the heart of Hemmant which remains one of the most highly sought after Industrial hubs. This near new freestander is situated approximately 12 radial kilometres from the Brisbane CBD providing excellent connectivity to the Gateway Motorway North and South and Brisbane Airport via the Port of Brisbane Motorway.

This investment offers the following keys features:

+ Term: 5 + 5 years
+ Annual Rental: $175,087* + outgoings + GST
+ Commencement date: 5th October 2018

- 1,210sqm* of high bay, clear span warehouse space offering min 8.5 meters clearance
- 290sqm* of CBD grade quality office space, split over two levels (fit out included)
- Male and Female amenities with separate shower + kitchen
- Dual container height, electric roller doors
- approx. 12 months old providing any owner occupier depreciation benefits
- High speed fibre connection to building
- Large concrete apron for container set down and/or extra parking
- Ample on-site parking (4 undercover bays)
- High definition CCTV installed and DVR in rack for recording
- Fully fenced and secured site with FOB security access

This opportunity is one not to be missed and offers fantastic value for any investor looking for a secured income stream.

For further information regarding this opportunity or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please contact Exclusive Agents Ben Lyons of CBRE today.
